dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text:
•  New look - Tap main menu to switch screens
•  Light and dark themes - See "Settings->Display" to change theme
•  L1/L5 signal labels - Carrier frequencies (CF) supported on certain devices with Android 8.0 and up
•  More SBAS - Inmarsat 3-F2 & 4-F3 and SES-5
•  Remove unnecessary permissions - These are no longer required for Google Maps
•  Bug fixes - See http://bit.ly/gpstest-releases

dynGuiComponents.name: android.widget.TextView
dynGuiComponents.text:
Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) - https://github.com/barbeau/gpstest/blob/master/FAQ.md

 *** Status View ***

•  Latitude - In decimal degrees (WGS 84)
•  Longitude - In decimal degrees (WGS 84)
•  Alt - Meters above the WGS 84 ellipsoid
•  Alt (MSL) - Meters above Mean Sea Level (requires NMEA support)
•  Acc - Estimated horizontal accuracy of the location (radius in meters of 68% confidence). In other words, if you draw a circle centered at this location
